law.history: Repealed and reenacted 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 51, sec. 139, effective July 15, 2010; and repealed 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 77, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 53, sec. 1, effective June 26, 2007; and ch. 137, sec. 139, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 220, sec. 1; and ch. 269, sec. 1. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 12, sec. 15. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2636-14.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Professional service corporations, professional limited liability companies, and partnerships -- Use of names -- Places of practice -- Limitation on number of practices per person.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2010). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2010 Ky. Acts ch.85 prevails over its repeal and reenactment in 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 51.
